---
layout: base.njk
title: Home
description: Personal software used to mean spreadsheets. Now it can mean much more. This blog explores the people using AI to build tools around their own lives.
---
<section class="space-y-10 lg:space-y-14">
  <section class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_18rem] lg:items-end">
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-amber-200/80">A publication about software people build for themselves</p>
      <div class="space-y-5">
        <h1 class="max-w-4xl font-serif text-5xl leading-none tracking-tight text-stone-50 sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">The Age of Personal Software</h1>
        <p class="max-w-2xl text-xl text-stone-300 sm:text-2xl">Personal software is evolving beyond spreadsheets.</p>
        <p class="max-w-3xl text-base leading-8 text-stone-400 sm:text-lg">Personal software used to mean spreadsheets. Now it can mean much more. This blog explores the people using AI to build tools around their own lives.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-3xl border border-amber-200/15 bg-amber-100/5 p-5 text-sm text-stone-300">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-amber-200/80">Focus</p>
      <p class="mt-3 leading-7">Minimal, readable stories about real tools built around real lives.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="posts" class="space-y-5">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 sm:flex-row sm:items-end sm:justify-between">
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-stone-500">Posts</p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-stone-100 sm:text-3xl">Latest writing</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="max-w-xl text-sm leading-7 text-stone-400">Essays on people using AI to make software that fits their own workflows better than off-the-shelf tools ever did.</p>
    </div>

    <ul class="grid gap-4">
      {% for post in collections.posts %}
        <li>
          <a href="{{ post.url | url }}" class="group block rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/4 p-6 transition duration-200 hover:border-amber-200/30 hover:bg-white/7">
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:justify-between">
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-stone-500">Essay {{ loop.index }}</p>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-stone-100 group-hover:text-amber-100">{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
                {% if post.data.description %}
                  <p class="max-w-3xl text-base leading-7 text-stone-400">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
                {% endif %}
              </div>
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-amber-200 group-hover:text-amber-100">Read →</span>
            </div>
          </a>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </section>
</section>
